WEBVTT

00:02:28.320 --> 00:02:31.656
It has been perverted
to mean violent struggle

00:02:31.680 --> 00:02:34.656
wherever Muslims
are undergoing difficulties,

00:02:34.680 --> 00:02:36.576
and turned into terrorism

00:02:36.600 --> 00:02:39.656
by fascistic Islamists like al-Qaeda,

00:02:39.680 --> 00:02:41.240
Islamic State and others.

00:02:42.280 --> 00:02:44.256
But I have come to understand

00:02:44.280 --> 00:02:48.216
that true jihad
means striving to the utmost

00:02:48.240 --> 00:02:51.600
to strengthen and live
those qualities which God loves:

00:02:52.440 --> 00:02:54.776
honesty, trustworthiness,

00:02:54.800 --> 00:02:56.896
compassion, benevolence,

00:02:56.920 --> 00:02:58.816
reliability, respect,

00:02:58.840 --> 00:03:00.216
truthfulness --